sql:
SELECT DISTINCT p.paper_id, p.title
FROM Paper p
JOIN Author_list al1 ON p.paper_id = al1.paper_id
JOIN Affiliation a1 ON al1.affiliation_id = a1.affiliation_id
JOIN Author_list al2 ON p.paper_id = al2.paper_id
JOIN Affiliation a2 ON al2.affiliation_id = a2.affiliation_id
WHERE a1.name = 'Stanford University' 
  AND a2.name = 'Columbia University'
  AND al1.author_id <> al2.author_id;
question: Find all papers with titles and paper IDs collaborated by Stanford University and Columbia University.

sql:
SELECT p.paper_id, p.title
FROM Paper p
WHERE p.paper_id IN (
    SELECT paper_id
    FROM Author_list
    WHERE affiliation_id = (SELECT affiliation_id FROM Affiliation WHERE name = 'Stanford University')
)
AND p.paper_id IN (
    SELECT paper_id
    FROM Author_list
    WHERE affiliation_id = (SELECT affiliation_id FROM Affiliation WHERE name = 'Columbia University')
)

sql:
SELECT p.paper_id, p.title
FROM Paper p
JOIN Author_list al ON p.paper_id = al.paper_id
JOIN Affiliation a ON al.affiliation_id = a.affiliation_id
WHERE a.name IN ('Stanford University', 'Columbia University')
GROUP BY p.paper_id, p.title
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT a.name) = 2;
question: Find all papers with titles and paper IDs collaborated by Stanford University and Columbia University.
